;Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================================================================================Main



Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點  這所小學就能完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子的復興也進行得很順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  朋友們不能來學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋被…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以朋友們沒法來學校了

Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第 9 話\N架往明日之橋


Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現異型軍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機進入戰鬥狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎樣的爬升啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝太前面了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋被…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害很小  別亂了陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一發要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對橋做了什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會  全軍攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:03:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到核心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢把橋給！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  辛苦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮藤也已經基本適應震電了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我還想再訓練下操控得更完美些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  就該是這氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天表現得很活躍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是平時的佩琳的話  被少佐表揚後肯定會說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  少佐  就是這樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多稱讚我一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之類的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我克洛斯特爾曼一族\N代代相傳的各種傳家寶現在也只剩下這把騎士劍了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只要把這個賣掉的話  就能湊夠修復那座橋梁的資金了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親  母親  我該怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳  沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊  突然扯著嗓子衝進別人的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…海…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明天大家一起到海邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  至少做下準備體操吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然就潑水過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  就算說是訓練  但絕對不允許掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒弄了  還請多加小心喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這項訓練啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要來嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不快給我跳下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不錯的天氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真有你的呢  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  這都是多虧了您平日的訓練指導…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防隨時可能出現的突發情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訓練結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好睏…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好久沒嘗試了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有佩琳在真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜你們所賜  連我都差點溺水了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好氣派的橋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:08:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  聽我說  海底下有一個箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還上著鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像寶箱一樣的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶箱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶箱嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確這片阿德利亞海從古至今都是海上貿易很興盛的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一兩個寶箱沉在海底也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  好像很有趣啊  麗奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  你們真的信寶箱這種蠢事的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是佩琳你說有的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底也只是可能性而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗奈  盧基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到極限了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  只要有這寶物在 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋梁就能！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳好慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒被吃了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你瞧  海底下不是有很多稀奇古怪的生物的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王烏賊啦  大王海參啦  大王海星之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快去找她才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異型軍？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰喵的說是異型軍啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼想要寶物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊… 寶物… 到手了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳！佩琳！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有聽到什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  橋梁完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳姐姐  多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面裝了什麼呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來動手的話就是小事一樁啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼呢  弗蘭西斯卡·盧基尼少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這寶物的使用方式早就已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出現了一個箱子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就代表裡面的東西是如此重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面肯定裝滿了金銀財寶…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有幾個箱子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼開都還是箱子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有出現寶物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能安靜點  這個肯定是最後一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被騙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然沒有寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子們不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩 佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊

Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 佩琳在為了橋而努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以從高盧回來樣子就一直很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然錢還是不會這麼輕易到手的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  就算放棄傳家之寶的騎士劍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 好像有奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明明什麼都沒有裡面卻會發出聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家附近有做這種東西的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是藏寶圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和地圖畫的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳能讀懂上面寫的字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是拉丁語吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀讀拉丁語不過是良家淑女一點小嗜好而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  佩琳恢復精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗奈  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵  像星空一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從洞窟入口射入的陽光被水面反射了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像哪一邊都能通到裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想走散的話就跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧基尼不見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說什麼要去抓魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了岩壁那邊就沒再回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我記得宮藤她們訓練之後也應該是去了岩壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆上的苔蘚在發光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎  看得見地圖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳加油  能看得懂地圖的就只有佩琳了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著從這裡一直往前走就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不安全嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之前有誰走過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進到這裡面去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進哪邊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分頭去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分開太危險了  從右邊去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人費心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是像探險一樣真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是人工造的洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們用作基地的地方  原本也是古代魔女的遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這洞窟也是它的一部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是很了不起的壺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的老前輩的技術麼  真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事怎麼都好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  沒事嗎美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點  美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這氣味是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 不是血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 美緒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…少佐  沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少…少佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜有點不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不能指揮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那可怕的聲音是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  藏起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是古代人的怨靈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦吧  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著啊  寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要走到哪兒去才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧盧基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點  在這光芒的前方一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是地圖上畫的寶貝的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯的  終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的石像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鐮倉大佛那麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像有點可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡  在那個石像的後面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡應該沉睡著寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  寶貝在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  孩子們的橋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  帥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧基尼好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石…石像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在架上橋之前  是不能放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是赤手空拳的確不太妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人  母親大人  還有高盧的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是寶物的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是香草…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁香還有月桂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧勒岡 藏紅花…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這個是胡椒…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這就是寶物…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼少佐會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這竟然就是我在找的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都只是香辛料而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的話也許是貴重的財產  現在全都是簡單就能到手的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些東西根本沒法成為高盧的復興資金來源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那份為高盧著想的心  才是最重要的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  盧基尼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮藤她們也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  走吧  哈特曼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們在幹啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說那裡是古代的遺跡  魔女為了保衛寶物而施的魔法大概還存留著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊佩琳的說不定就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事真是讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  這個  寄給佩琳的信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是從高盧寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是橋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起建造的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合大家的力量建起的橋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說不定就是真正的復興呢  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:22:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也要盡快打倒異形軍  然後再回高盧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  到時我會給你們做嚮導的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚火辣辣的疼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.91,0:22:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法穿褲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼  真是謎團眾多的基地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來  中佐怎麼了？


Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.57,0:24:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  哈特曼  你的擊墜數是多少架來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3  不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.24,0:24:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  Strike Witches 2
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,500 overs
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.40,0:24:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是多少架啊…
